Check list for releasing new versions of DOLFIN
-----------------------------------------------

(Assuming the current version number is 0.2.0.)

1. Edit the file ChangeLog using proper formatting

2. Change the version number in configure.in

3. Commit changes to cvs and do

	cvs rtag v0_2_0 dolfin

4. Checkout a clean version and run the script

	scripts/makedist

   Remember to check the output in make-*.log

5. Update the web page with the version number and the release date

6. Update at freshmeat

That should be all...
